{
  "stem": "7592.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So five guys-- you have to look for four more guys to go with you to the latrine, because everybody was responsible for another one.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There always was a [INAUDIBLE] over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hanging.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By hanging, by shooting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was a place over there which they called this in Polish-- it's not a nice word-- Hujowa Gorka.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hujowa Gorka.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They mention the book too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a hill and around the hill was like graves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they put over [INAUDIBLE] and shot them with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later they came with gasoline, put fire, burn them over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was daily, because they brought from outside people, too, which they find outside somebody, and they brought him over there, and this was everyday.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Frequent hanging, frequent shooting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You got the-- you came to camp, and then, oh, he got today shot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This guy got hanged, this, and this, and that's-- so everybody feeling as long as it's not me, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As much-- because, sure, you want-- people came over there and sold you cigarettes, which they got from outside.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You gave him bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was business, you know, all day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Since 19-- through 1944, until November when we went to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything loose over there, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't watch so much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The roll calls-- because Goth was gone, and everybody felt that something is going-- the war is to end.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the bad guys tried to be nice all of a sudden, because if they survive and the is over, they're going to pay for the things--",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took him out after they find out he killed his six, seven people without Berlin's order.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was all the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
